    <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Kulfi brands, ice cream parlours adding kulfi to their menu, and seasonal vendors who want to increase production during summer months (March–August). The ROI on kulfi machines is typically highest during peak summer when a single cart can sell 200–500 kulfis per day.</p>

